Copied from http://code.google.com/p/colorpickerjs/


Modifications:

moved *.js, *.css and image files to proper folders (javascript/colorpicker, stylesheets/colorpicker and images/colorpicker)
changed IMAGE_BASE from 'img/' to 'images/colorpicker/' in colorpicker.js

use the colorpicker like this:

# my_thing_controller.rb
class MyThingController
  helper ColorPickerHelper
  # ...
  # ...
end

# myview.html.erb
<input type="text" id="colorfield1" value="FF33FF">
<%= color_picker_tag "colorfield1" %>

